What is derived
---------------
The include/ctll/ directory (the CTLL compile-time LL(1) parser,
ctll::fixed_string and supporting headers) is copied from notre, where
it descends from Hana Dusikova's CTRE with modifications. The build and
packaging scaffolding follows the sibling projects compile-time-json
and compile-time-json5 (https://github.com/alexios-angel/). The XML
grammar, parse table, document types, semantic actions and the ctxml
API are original to this repository, but follow the architecture CTRE
established (a Tablewright-generated LL(1) table driven by CTLL with
semantic actions building a type-level result).

The parse table include/ctxml/xml.hpp is generated from
include/ctxml/xml.gram by Tablewright
(https://github.com/alexios-angel/Tablewright).

